@khăng khăng
- Persist in
=ốm nhưng cứ khăng khăng lên đường+To persist in taking the road though sick

@khăn gói
- Lagre handkerchief (to make a bundle of clothes, etc. with)
=Cho mấy bộ áo quần vào khăn gói+To bundle a few changes of clothes in a large handkerchief

@khăm
- Nasty
=Chơi khăm ai+To play a nasty trick on someone

@khăng khít
* adj
- to be attached; devoted to
